com.ge.dspmicro.mqttriver.send.api

Interface IMqttRiverConfig


  • public interface IMqttRiverConfig
    Configurations for MQTT River service.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_BROKER
      [Required] The broker is primarily responsible for receiving all messages, filtering them, decide who is interested in it and then sending the message to all subscribed clients.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_CLIENT_ID
      [Required] The client identifier (short ClientId) is an identifier of each MQTT client connecting to a MQTT broker.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_INTERVAL
      [Optional] Heart beat interval in seconds to check the connection.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_PASSWORD
      [Optional] Password for authentication if the broker requires.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_QOS
      [Required] An agreement between sender and receiver of a message regarding the guarantees of delivering a message.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_TOPIC
      [Required] A topic is a UTF-8 string, which is used by the broker to filter messages for each connected client.
      static String PROPKEY_MQTT_USER_NAME
      [Optional] User name for authentication if the broker requires.
      static String PROPKEY_RIVER_NAME
      [Required] Property key for the river name.
